Detailed Description

cvmx_tofb_tx::_ila_0_3

This register stores octets 0 to 3 of the ILA sequence to transmit. The octets are stored in big-endian order, i.e., octet 0 is stored in bits <31:24>, octet 1 in bits <23:16>, etc.
